# Load Test Results Directory

This directory stores load test results and reports.

## Files Generated

- `summary.json` - k6 test summary
- `report.html` - Artillery HTML report
- `results-*.json` - Node.js load test results

## Viewing Results

### k6 Results
```bash
cat results/summary.json
```

### Artillery HTML Report
```bash
# Open in browser
start results/report.html  # Windows
open results/report.html   # Mac
xdg-open results/report.html  # Linux
```

### Node.js Load Test
Results are displayed in console and saved to:
```bash
cat results/node-load-test-*.json
```
